text: Sagittarius could mean: *Sagittarius (constellation) *Sagittarius (astrology), an astrological sign *Sagittarius dwarf elliptical galaxy *Sagittarius (band), a 60's California recording project featuring Gary Usher and Curt Boettcher *Sagittarius (comics), a member of a fictional evil organization called Zodiac. *Sagittarius (Russian TV children channel), a member who had in Saint Petersburg kids children channel. *Sagittarii were Roman mounted archers. *Sagittarii (gladiators) were Roman mounted-archer gladiators.
title: Sagittarius
